# CODEOWNERS file
# 
# This file defines code ownership for different parts of the repository.
# When a pull request is opened, the specified owners will be automatically
# requested as reviewers.
#
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Syntax:
#   <pattern> <owner1> <owner2> ... <ownerN>
#
# Patterns support:
#   - Glob patterns (e.g., *.swift, Models/**)
#   - @username or @team-name for GitHub users/teams
#   - Use @org/team-name for organization teams

